      "text": "Scho wiſſu eſmu es re-\ndſejs/ un greeſu mannu Sirde\nuhs wiſſu Darbu/ kas noteek ap-\npakſch Saules. Daschkahrt weens\nZilweſs pahr ohtru walda fewim\npar faunn.\n"
